Careers at Hilliard Lyons
 
Outstanding compensation, benefits, and growth opportunities - as well as a famously collegial culture. Management that is experienced, in-touch and actively involved. A regional financial services firm with smart plans for growth. Read on to find out more about why Hilliard Lyons is one of the best choices the best professionals can make. 


 
Stable
Steadfast priorities—such as a devotion to providing the finest in client service—have earned us a reputation as a superb financial services firm, one of the most respected in the industry.
We are grounded by our 160-year history as a regional firm with its headquarters in Louisville, Kentucky and 70+ offices in 12 states. Our company has experienced the Industrial Revolution, the Depression, wartimes and peacetimes, market booms and market busts. With experience has come wisdom and strength.
Growing
Hilliard Lyons is in the midst of one of the most dynamic periods in its history.
Companywide, we are actively devoting resources to growth. We are thinking entrepreneurially, deepening our knowledge and skill sets, and striving for even greater levels of performance - all while remaining true to the strong Hilliard Lyons tradition.
We have developed and are constantly perfecting the ability to provide complete, holistic wealth management to our clients. These services include financial planning; portfolio management; trust services and estate planning; investment banking; and capital markets, public finance, and lending services.
We know that the skills, abilities, and commitment of our people are the driving force in our continued success.
 
 






